            <lg xml:id="TK643">
<l>kēṭṭārp piṇikkuntakaiyavāyk kēḷārum </l>
<l> vēṭpa moḻivatāñ col</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The (minister's) speech is that which seeks (to express) elements as bind his friends (to himself) and is so delivered as to make even his enemies desire (his friendship).</l>
